					    <article id="post-8675" class="post-8675 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-by-anthony-tao category-general tag-featured tag-liu-xia tag-liu-xiaobo tag-video clearfix" role="article">
						
						    <header class="article-header">
							
							    <h3 class="h2"><a href="http://beijingcream.com/2012/12/watch-chinese-activists-push-past-security-to-visit-liu-xia/" rel="bookmark" title="Watch: Chinese Activists Push Past Security To Visit Liu Xia, Wife Of Liu Xiaobo [UPDATE]">Watch: Chinese Activists Push Past Security To Visit Liu Xia, Wife Of Liu Xiaobo [UPDATE]</a></h3>
                  <p class="byline vcard">By <span class="author"><a href="http://beijingcream.com/category/by-anthony-tao" title="Posts by Anthony Tao" rel="author">Anthony Tao</a></span> <time class="updated" datetime="2012-12-31" pubdate>December 31, 2012 7:02 pm</time> &nbsp; Comments: <a href="http://beijingcream.com/2012/12/watch-chinese-activists-push-past-security-to-visit-liu-xia/#comments">0</a></p>
						
						    </header> <!-- end article header -->
					
						    <section class="entry-content clearfix">
                                                        <div style="float: left;">
                                                                <a href="http://beijingcream.com/2012/12/watch-chinese-activists-push-past-security-to-visit-liu-xia/"><img width="150" height="150" src="http://beijingcream.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/Liu-Xia-video-150x150.jpeg" class="attachment-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="Liu Xia video" /></a>
                                                        </div>
                                                        On Friday, December 28 -- the birthday of jailed Nobel Peace Prize recipient Liu Xiaobo -- a group of activists made a daring visit to the residence of his wife, Liu Xia, currently under house arrest.

You can watch them in the above video, uploaded yesterday to the YouTube account of Hu Jia, activist/dissident and director of the June Fourth Heritage and Culture Association. Hu writes that he and Hao Jian, Liu Di and Xu Youyu, among others, arrived at about 9 pm and basically overpowered a surprised guard.<!--
                                                        &nbsp;<span class='read-more'><a href='http://beijingcream.com/2012/12/watch-chinese-activists-push-past-security-to-visit-liu-xia/'>Read more »</a></span>
-->
