							    <h3 class="h2"><a href="http://beijingcream.com/2012/12/pandas-might-be-source-of-powerful-new-antibiotic/" rel="bookmark" title="Pandas might be source of powerful new antibiotic">Pandas might be source of powerful new antibiotic</a></h3>
                  <p class="byline vcard">By <span class="author"><a href="http://beijingcream.com/category/by-anthony-tao" title="Posts by Anthony Tao" rel="author">Anthony Tao</a></span> <time class="updated" datetime="2012-12-30" pubdate>December 30, 2012 4:57 pm</time> &nbsp; Comments: <a href="http://beijingcream.com/2012/12/pandas-might-be-source-of-powerful-new-antibiotic/#comments">0</a></p>
						
